Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:24.34,CN-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}即便相隔甚遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:27.17,CN-ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我也不會忘記
